han half of scientists endorsed global warming, it does not necessarily mean that the other half dismiss the concept entirely. There may be varying degrees of agreement and disagreement among scientists on the issue of global warming, and it's important to consider the complexity and nuances of the issue when evaluating the claim.\"\n"label: true
