 impact of palm oil plantations on biodiversity can also vary depending on factors such as the type of land use before the plantation was established and the management practices used in the plantation. Therefore, a more nuanced understanding of the potential impacts of renewable energy technologies and land use changes are needed to address these issues effectively\\\"\"\n"label: false
